                        </a></div></div><ol class="sense_single" htag="ol"><li class="sense" htag="li" id="autismspectrum_sng_1" hclass="sense"><span class="sensetop" htag="span" hclass="sensetop"><span class="def" htag="span" hclass="def">a range of conditions affecting brain development that can be severe or mild. People on the <span class="dh">autism spectrum</span> can find it difficult to communicate and form relationships, and may show repeated or limited patterns of thought and behaviour.</span></span><ul class="examples" htag="ul" hclass="examples"><li class="" htag="li"><span class="x">The writer was herself on the autism spectrum.</span></li><li class="" htag="li"><span class="x">Their three children are all on the autistic spectrum.</span></li><li class="" htag="li"><span class="x">She has some special needs such as sensory sensitivities that suggest the autism spectrum.</span></li></ul>    <div id="ring-links-box">
